sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant I as Ingestion Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant A as Analytics Engine
    participant CH as ClickHouse
    participant R as Redis
    participant AN as Anomaly Service
    participant N as Notification Service

    U->>G: POST /api/v1/transactions/ingest (CSV)
    G->>I: Internal Route
    I->>I: Normalize via Adapter
    I->>DB: Persist UnifiedTransactions
    I->>A: Trigger Analytics (REST)
    A->>A: Compute FHS & Aggregates
    A->>CH: Insert History/Trends (Async)
    A->>R: Invalidate Cache
    A->>AN: Notify Completion (Webhook)
    AN->>R: Read Baselines
    AN->>AN: Compute Z-Score
    alt is Anomaly (|Z| > 2.5)
        AN->>N: Create Alert
        N->>G: Push WebSocket Alert
        G->>U: Browser Toast Notification
    end
    I-->>U: 202 Accepted {ingested: N}
